Forgotten Fields Gameplay (PC HD) [1080p60FPS]
KickStarter - https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/forgotten-fields/forgotten-fields-0?ref=8krl1i
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1296980/Forgotten_Fields/

PC Specs:
CPU: Intel Kaby Lake, Core i7 7700K 4.20GHz
Motherboard: MSI Z270 GAMING PRO 
Memory: Corsair Vengeance LPX Black 32GB DDR4
HDD: WD Black 4TB SATA-III 7200RPM 128MB

Game Information:
Forgotten Fields is a game about a struggling author who travels back to his childhood home one last time before it's sold off. Visit old friends, relive memories and experience bursts of inspiration in this nostalgic game about the passage of time.
